":"2018-07-29T05:52:55.000Z","msg":"好撚多風打 &gt;&gt; 中 ，仲要嘢嘢食到正，呢兩日又嚟一個仲要掃晒關東中部關西<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n平均溫度高 &gt;&gt; 又中，之前直頭破紀錄41點幾度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n呢個天文台真係好撚嘢<br />\n準撚過佢老母嚟M<br />\n其實叫啲日本仔睇香港天文台做人得啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d7a2001cc9be290b149081ad7d80d0f68668566","tid":746801,"uid":48222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T05:54:21.000Z","msg":"渣GA"},{"pid":"37c4722b38633b5e324d903879ec97f920e8ac1c","tid":746801,"uid":188,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T08:09:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1497d93d5dfc9491e1aa67cd97a2da29d964d01a","tid":746801,"uid":185258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"40e8ef6ddd795cfb229c4c2c34fa21b8e7539b2d","tid":746801,"uid":11973,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T05:45:58.000Z","msg":"懷疑佢部超級電腦連氣象雷達全套其實搬撚咗去日本<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T08:10:54.000Z","msg":"部超級電腦用左大陸晶片"},{"pid":"fe821454f4aaa8dbee9afb63f03223e377b6a5c4","tid":746801,"uid":188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T04:02:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"628b7b18293a013b2b40db3e8af7d78336afdbe8","tid":746801,"uid":1221,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T04:27:59.000Z","msg":"9up靠估台"},{"pid":"21745fa0f72bbf340537b722a00c571146c48037","tid":746801,"uid":66943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"66c78f5a7e347688cc1331c29d61abe8d20fe64c","tid":746801,"uid":188,"like":97,"dislike":3,"score":94,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T04:23:58.000Z","msg":"天文台超級電腦=黃金$4000打機list"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T04:35:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"629fb067f78dba537dba4d73bf1ad83dbb2ecb36","tid":746801,"uid":34773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T04:37:01.000Z","msg":"唔好咁老定，最後８日打８個風<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ce818c5f5e74b89bdf8335d204d2216a06fa227","tid":746801,"uid":113000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T04:38:40.000Z","msg":"秋天都到啦<br />\n<br />\n仲風乜鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"793bbb49d3d91644f7b82d879e0c149232a57ded","tid":746801,"uid":197052,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T04:39:01.000Z","msg":"肯打未姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d865a2711eb34f1b97de640d579319dbead92aaf","tid":746801,"uid":6752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T04:42:49.000Z","msg":"準到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a1a709ef45a9c323383ac45440b8c800796b4fa","tid":746801,"uid":87925,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"quote":{"pid":"6bd89d4df5337801798b77c2f68a8257a644dde2","tid":746801,"uid":1251,"like":43,"dislike":1,"score":42,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T04:27:50.000Z","msg":"連幾個鐘後既雨勢都預測唔到仲學人預測一年既事<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T04:43:13.000Z","msg":"屌，大交合都好信? <br />\n佢地根本已經由預測天氣，變為實時天氣報導好耐啦 <br />\n<br />\n同一個預測報足佢 7 x 24，唔中就彈弓手，見出面好天就改做天晴，大雨嗰時就掛個暴雨警告，停雨就話你知部份地區多雲 / 有陽光 / 有驟雨，點知唔夠兩個鐘又落過狗屎，就咋咋淋掛返個暴雨警告出嚟攞尾彩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n平時話咩有一道冷峰 / 低壓槽 / 高壓脊 / 雷雨帶接近本港，叫大家小心 <br />\n你以為真係睇天氣圖，靠數據預測呀? 咪又係睇鄰近地區天氣報導咋 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n見到珠三角天氣報導話而家有大雨，就出段警告話有雷雨帶嚟緊，可能影響本港 <br />\n見到廣州天氣報導話而家有落雪，就出段警告話有寒流嚟緊，大家著多件衫 <br />\n<br />\n嚟得太快，改唔撚切 D&quot;天氣預測&quot;，就話係極端天氣影響 / 天氣變化變幻莫測，就算係最精密嘅科技都未必可以準確預測，所以大條道理估唔撚中 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n屌你老味，我仲以為自己睇緊風水節目，最尾出嗰句「玄學並非精密科學，節目內容只供參考」咋 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n呢 D咁嘅渣流攤預測，係古時唔撚洗推出午門都要發配充軍啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4c473fe872d459a8b0467afd2e76d21ee7ed21c","tid":746801,"uid":33174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T04:46:05.000Z","msg":"仲有澳狗信足大交合嫁"},{"pid":"977a59b59299f283b2cc943ba1ccb4582ec2572e","tid":746801,"uid":87925,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a4c473fe872d459a8b0467afd2e76d21ee7ed21c","tid":746801,"uid":33174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T04:46:05.000Z","msg":"仲有澳狗信足大交合嫁"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T05:15:56.000Z","msg":"究竟馬交定香港大交合廢D<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50bd37aa9e23ee53d0c128ddd768b4cc0908b35f","tid":746801,"uid":188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T04:12:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 準 又中"},{"pid":"7a01fcb81ce6d00558ca5015a355f928cd7bdcb5","tid":746801,"uid":188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T02:18:35.000Z","msg":"又中"},{"pid":"c2611b70dc132d43fba1c28f8019ee7fd9b045cc","tid":746801,"uid":14075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T03:41:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\